<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Services — <%- site.businessName %></title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/services-page.css">
</head>
<body>

  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <!-- PAGE HERO -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-inner">
      <span class="section-label">Employment Law Services</span>
      <h1>What we do</h1>
      <p>We specialise in employment law and provide expert advice across a broad range of workplace issues. Whether you're facing dismissal, dispute, or discrimination, we're here to help.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES GRID -->
  <section class="services-overview">
    <div class="services-overview-inner">
      
      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="service-item-header">
          <h3>Unfair Dismissal</h3>
        </div>
        <p>If you've been dismissed and believe it was unjustified, you may have grounds for a personal grievance. We can help you understand your rights and take action.</p>
        <a href="/services/unfair-dismissal" class="service-link">Learn more →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="service-item-header">
          <h3>Disciplinary Meeting</h3>
        </div>
        <p>Facing a disciplinary meeting can be stressful. Knowing your rights before you walk in the door can make all the difference. We can prepare you or attend with you.</p>
        <a href="/services/disciplinary-meeting" class="service-link">Learn more →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="service-item-header">
          <h3>90 Day Trial Dismissal</h3>
        </div>
        <p>Being dismissed under a 90 day trial period doesn't always mean your employer acted lawfully. A trial period must meet strict legal requirements to be valid.</p>
        <a href="/services/90-day-trial-dismissal" class="service-link">Learn more →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="service-item-header">
          <h3>Redundancy</h3>
        </div>
        <p>Redundancy must be genuine. If your employer used restructuring as a pretext to get rid of you, or failed to follow a fair process, you may have a strong claim.</p>
        <a href="/services/redundancy" class="service-link">Learn more →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="service-item-header">
          <h3>Workplace Bullying</h3>
        </div>
        <p>Workplace bullying is serious, damaging, and unlawful. You don't have to endure it. We can help you take action and hold your employer accountable.</p>
        <a href="/services/workplace-bullying" class="service-link">Learn more →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="service-item-header">
          <h3>Sexual Harassment</h3>
        </div>
        <p>Sexual harassment in the workplace is unlawful and deeply harmful. You have the right to work in an environment free from this behaviour. We handle every case with sensitivity.</p>
        <a href="/services/sexual-harassment" class="service-link">Learn more →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="service-item-header">
          <h3>Medical Termination</h3>
        </div>
        <p>Being dismissed because of a medical condition or illness is difficult. In many cases it is also unlawful. We help you understand your rights and take action.</p>
        <a href="/services/medical-termination" class="service-link">Learn more →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="service-item-header">
          <h3>Unpaid Wages</h3>
        </div>
        <p>If your employer has failed to pay you correctly — whether through withheld wages, unpaid overtime, or incorrect holiday pay — we can help you recover what you're owed.</p>
        <a href="/services/unpaid-wages" class="service-link">Learn more →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="service-item-header">
          <h3>Migrant Exploitation</h3>
        </div>
        <p>Migrant workers are among the most vulnerable to exploitation. If you have been underpaid or mistreated because of your visa status, we can help you safely.</p>
        <a href="/services/migrant-exploitation" class="service-link">Learn more →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="service-item-header">
          <h3>Personal Grievance</h3>
        </div>
        <p>A personal grievance is the formal process for resolving employment disputes in New Zealand. If you've been treated unfairly at work, this may be the right tool.</p>
        <a href="/services/personal-grievance" class="service-link">Learn more →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="service-item-header">
          <h3>Exit Packages</h3>
        </div>
        <p>When an employment relationship comes to an end, the terms of your exit can have a significant impact. We help you negotiate the best possible package.</p>
        <a href="/services/exit-packages" class="service-link">Learn more →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="service-item">
        <div class="service-item-header">
          <h3>Other Issues</h3>
        </div>
        <p>Not sure if you have a case? Don't think your situation fits into one category neatly? Talk to us today about advice and your options.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="service-link">Contact Us</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA SECTION -->
  <section class="services-cta">
    <div class="services-cta-inner">
      <span class="section-label">Not sure which service you need?</span>
      <h2>Get a free consultation</h2>
      <p>Every employment situation is unique. Contact us today for a free, no obligation consultation. We'll listen to your situation and advise you on your options.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Get in touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>

  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
